CHAOS UNDIVIDED — SDDM Theme
==============================

  "In the grim darkness of the far future, there is only war."
  "And also a login screen."

DESCRIPTION
-----------
A Warhammer 40K Chaos-themed SDDM greeter. On every boot, one of the four
Chaos Gods (or Chaos Undivided) is randomly chosen and the entire theme
shifts to match — colors, titles, quotes, glows, and ember particles all
reflect whichever dark patron has blessed your session.

  Khorne      — Blood red. Skulls. War.
  Tzeentch    — Arcane blue. Schemes within schemes.
  Nurgle      — Plague green. Grandfather's embrace.
  Slaanesh    — Hedonist purple. Perfection through excess.
  Undivided   — Tarnished gold. All gods. All chaos.

FEATURES
--------
  - Random Chaos God selection on each load
  - 30 rising ember/ash particle effects
  - Warp ambient glow bloom (top + bottom)
  - Scanline overlay for corrupted terminal aesthetic
  - Hostname glitch effect on failed login
  - Blood-red screen flash on failed login
  - Scrolling 40K lore ticker at the bottom
  - Breathing panel border glow
  - Slowly rotating chaos sigil
  - Per-god flavor quotes and taglines

REQUIREMENTS
------------
  - SDDM
  - Qt 5.x / QtQuick 2.0+
  - Cinzel font (for gothic lettering)

    Install Cinzel on Arch Linux:
      wget "https://fonts.google.com/download?family=Cinzel" -O /tmp/cinzel.zip
      sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/share/fonts/cinzel
      sudo unzip /tmp/cinzel.zip -d /usr/local/share/fonts/cinzel
      sudo fc-cache -fv

INSTALLATION
------------
  sudo cp -r chaos-undivided/ /usr/share/sddm/themes/
  # then set Theme=chaos-undivided in /etc/sddm.conf

  Or via sddm settings in your DE.

TESTING
-------
  sddm-greeter --test-mode --theme /usr/share/sddm/themes/chaos-undivided

FILES
-----
  Main.qml          — Main theme logic and layout
  theme.conf        — Theme configuration (background path etc.)
  metadata.desktop  — Theme metadata for SDDM
  background.jpg    — Background wallpaper (chaos star on void black)
  rectangle.png     — Retained from base theme (unused, kept for compat)
  angle-down.png    — Dropdown arrow icon for session/layout selectors
  LICENSE           — MIT License

